Package: libptb0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: PowerTab and GuitarPro file parsing library
 A PowerTab and GuitarPro file parsing library.

Package: libptb-dev
Architecture: all
Depends: libptb0=${Source-Version}
Description: Development files for libptb0
 Header files for the PowerTab and GuitarPro parser library.

Package: ptabtools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Tools for parsing PowerTab files
 This package contains a utilities for using PowerTab and GuitarPro files
 on Linux. It includes utilities for converting PowerTab files to 
 to GNU LilyPond files, plain ASCII files and MusicXML files. 
 It also contains a library that can be used by other programs 
 for reading PowerTab and GuitarPro files.
